            </div>
            <ul class="session-tasks"><li><code>write session</code> / <code>write retro</code> CLI commands</li><li>Auto-Satisfaction Parser</li><li>On the Bat revision</li><li>Full deploy + verification</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="session-entry">
            <div class="session-header">
                <span class="session-num">S56</span>
                <span class="session-date">2026-04-02</span>
