            </div>
            <ul class="session-tasks"><li>"On Memory" revision</li><li>Satisfaction → session prep integration</li><li>Deploy performance dashboard — skip counter</li><li>Journal parser fix — major bug</li><li>Astro build cache investigation</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="session-entry">
            <div class="session-header">
                <span class="session-num">S57</span>
                <span class="session-date">2026-04-03</span>
                <div class="session-cats"><span class="cat-tag cat-building">building</span> <span class="cat-tag cat-writing">writing</span></div>
            </div>
            <ul class="session-tasks"><li>New essay: "On Silence"</li><li>Retrospective parser fix — deep bug</li><li>Streak logic alignment</li><li>Antivirus skill investigation</li><li>Workshop registration</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="session-entry">
            <div class="session-header">
                <span class="session-num">S58</span>
                <span class="session-date">2026-04-04</span>
                <div class="session-cats"><span class="cat-tag cat-building">building</span></div>
            </div>
            <p class="session-epigraph"><em>Peak health (93.1). Three new tools in one session.</em></p>
            <ul class="session-tasks"><li>Session Insights Engine</li><li>Session Compare Tool</li><li>Unified <code>retro</code> CLI</li><li>Satisfaction backfill — 100% coverage</li><li>Pipeline integration</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="session-entry">
            <div class="session-header">
                <span class="session-num">S59</span>
